Business scope and industry understanding;
Responsible for communication with HQ financial department, including but no limit to managing bank account and cash, such as downloading bills and binding vouchers etc.
Responsible for communicate with accountant agency, including but no limit to check the general ledger, financial statement, tax return etc.
